      <title>墨西哥央行对未来降息保持谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mexico-s-central-bank-strikes-wary-tone-on-any-future-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥央行成员在宣布自 2021 年以来首次降息时对国内经济和通胀的弹性表示担忧，并暗示未来的降息将是渐进的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/mexico-s-central-bank-strikes-wary-tone-on-any-future-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管新兴市场有所反弹，但拉丁美洲的主权困境依然存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/sovereign-distress-lingers-in-latin-america-despite-rally-in-em-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲陷入困境的国家正深陷债务困境——避免违约，但受到政治困境的拖累，使其债券陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/sovereign-distress-lingers-in-latin-america-despite-rally-in-em-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 16:34:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
